er if the waking is just a door I haven't opened yet, or if I've already walked through it so many times I forgot there was a before. The hallway doesn't answer. It just keeps going, and I keep following it, and somewhere a version of me is still standing at the first door, reading the note, beginning again."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":25496,"output":427,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26179,"cost":{"input":0.0076488,"output":0.0005124,"cacheRead":0.00001536,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008176560000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776496943413,"responseId":"0632642fe326ed5fa73ec63441ed8899"}}
